{"id": 1981, "genre": 1000, "title": "现在让你花钱健身的种种尝试里，你觉得哪些才是真正解决问题的？", "description": "既然传统健身房让你各种不满意，那你想要什么样的健身房嘞？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 10734, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171029184506RtSa5fCZNuePrQV3.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-30T17:00:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 3200, "title": "现在让你花钱健身的种种尝试里，你觉得哪些才是真正解决问题的？", "content": "现在让你花钱健身的种种尝试里，你觉得哪些才是真正解决问题的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 245078, "content": "卡和私教的价格都是透明和固定的，不用和销售扯皮", "image": "img/option/option/20171029185821BSjsNO31crb7px95.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245079, "content": "延长营业时间，照顾加班人士", "image": "img/option/option/20171030153655P1jWrb3pIuNV6cyB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245080, "content": "除了年卡，还有月卡和次卡可以选择", "image": "img/option/option/20171029190408jJ6ykBpgdNqez1D8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245081, "content": "规模不用很大，但希望分店够多，最好就在公司楼下", "image": "img/option/option/201710291905237GlznwWyxM1v5L4S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245089, "content": "原来的瑜伽老三样好乏味，多一些好玩的时髦的课程会更吸引我", "image": "img/option/option/20171029204817uRjB6rV7d9Xb2kIw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245090, "content": "自己准备健身餐太麻烦，希望健身房那里能买到配好的", "image": "img/option/option/201710292049216BrYjX0MmoGIndcN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245239, "content": "有水吧或者自动售货机，提供多样化饮品选择", "image": "img/option/option/2017103017110038CKSOJGsYEqVBa7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245238, "content": "小点没事，希望人少，不用等器械，以及有专属储物柜那种", "image": "img/option/option/20171030170859owNp47vxmha9qDtb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}